---- Run the script-----

1. Goto Linux Terminal
2. execute file in bash
    $bash filename.sh
3. to save the filename 
4. chmod u+x filename.sh
5. if path problem occured then
    $cd ~
    $mkdir ~/bin
    copy the file to ~/bin
6. execute 
    $filename.sh
   or
    $./filename.sh

For details and feedback
blog: <http://kwind415.blogspot.com>

